    If has_const is equal to 1:
        If has_cmp is equal to 1:
            If has_branch is equal to 1:
                Return 1
            End If
        End If
    End If
    Return 0
End Process

@Reasoning:
check_sigmoid_pattern recognises sigmoid = 1 / (1 + exp(-x)). Its distinctive
MIR markers are a transcendental exp call (a MIR_CALL 20304 to an exp intrinsic)
combined with a division (MIR_DIV 20005) and an addition (MIR_ADD 20002) of a
constant one - a single exp feeding a single reciprocal.
