@Reasoning:
check_transpose_pattern recognises a matrix transpose: a doubly-nested loop that
loads from [i][j] and stores to [j][i] with the index roles swapped. The
conservative marker is two loop levels carrying both a load-class and a
store-class instruction (a pure index-permuting copy with no arithmetic).
