multiply or add arithmetic in the body (transpose only permutes, it does not
compute). Returns 1 when all conditions hold; 0 otherwise.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints:
O(n) single pass plus the loop count. No allocation.
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope:
Pure read; conservative 0 when the index-swap copy shape is absent.
